channel.title: Exercises: Git :: Introduction to Web Dev
channel.description: We will use our new terminal powers to move through the Git exercises. In whichever directory you are keeping your coursework outside of javascript-projects, make a new directory called Git-Exercises using the mkdir command. You want to make sure this is outside of javascript-projects because it will cause an issue if you try and make a new Git repository inside an existing one. Check your solution My-Computer:my-coursework myusername$ mkdir Git-Exercises
